Subject:  Re: [PATCH V7 1/2] dma-mapping: Rework dma_get_cache_alignment()
<span class="quote">
 
&gt; index aba7138..e2c5d9e 100644</span>
<span class="quote">&gt; --- a/arch/mips/include/asm/dma-mapping.h</span>
